.env*.local

# File-mode runtime data — created by the File*Repository classes and
# test runs. Not a committable artifact.
data/

# Build-time mirror of `workshop-content/agenda.json` copied by
# `scripts/copy-agenda-source.mjs` so Turbopack (which does not
# honour `experimental.externalDir`) can resolve the import during
# `next build`. Regenerated by the `pre{build,dev,test}` hook.
lib/__generated__/
